Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:25.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想象着一个无尽的浩瀚宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}who envisioned an infinitely grander cosmos.
