Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:47.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们发现自己并不是宇宙的中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when we first realize we're not the center of the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们以外还有更广大的世界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we belong to something much greater than ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我们成长所需经历的一部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's part of growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:55.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为每个人都会经历到这段过程\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And as it happens to each of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.44,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的文明也在16世纪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so it began to happen to our civilization
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.44,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也经历着这样的成长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the 16th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:02.05,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想象一下望远镜问世之前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Imagine a world before telescopes,
