Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:15.99,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都围绕着我们运行  然后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}revolved around us... and then...
