Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:30.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多人 例如宗教改革发起人马丁·路德\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Many, like the Protestant reformer Martin Luther,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:33.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}认为这是在对圣经的可耻侮辱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}took this idea as a scandalous affront to Scripture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.41,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们震怒了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They were horrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:39.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是另一个人却认为哥白尼说的不全面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But for one man, Copernicus didn't go far enough.
