Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:44.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他生性反叛\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and he was a natural-born rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:47.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他渴望打破这狭隘宇宙的枷锁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He longed to bust out of that cramped little universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:50.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那不勒斯做道明会的修道士时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even as a young Dominican monk in Naples,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他就与这个世界格格不入\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he was a misfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当时在意大利没有思想的自由\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This was a time when there was no freedom of thought in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是布鲁诺渴望了解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But Bruno hungered to know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关于上帝创世的一切\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}everything about God's creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:00.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他阅读了被教廷禁止的书籍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He dared to read the books banned by the Church,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从此踏上了不归路\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that was his undoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:05.17,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些书籍中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In one of them,
