Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:09.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI}物性论 - 卢克·莱修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:12.28,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}向他描述了一个更广阔的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}whispered to him of a universe far greater,
