Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.82,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想象站在宇宙的边缘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to imagine standing at the edge of the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:25.82,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}向外射出一支箭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and shooting an arrow outward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:28.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果箭继续前进 那么很明显\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If the arrow keeps going, then clearly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:31.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙继续向所谓的边缘以外延伸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the universe extends beyond what you thought was the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:33.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是如果箭不继续前进\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But if the arrow doesn't keep going...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.17,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比方说 撞在一堵墙上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}say it hits a wall... then that wall must lie
