Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:42.47,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么如果你站在这堵墙上向外射箭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now if you stand on that wall and shoot another arrow,
