Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要么是飞入无尽的太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it either flies forever out into space,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:49.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要么是撞在某个障碍物上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or it hits some boundary
