Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.99,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无论如何 宇宙是没有界限的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Either way, the universe is unbounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:58.29,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙必然是无尽的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The cosmos must be infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.79,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}布鲁诺深以为然\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This made perfect sense to Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:03.16,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他崇拜的上帝是全能的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The God he worshiped was infinite.
