Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:43.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这个梦中 他认识到了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In this dream, he awakened to a world
